Author:
mucbj0 file:///D:/anwend/java/JDepend-2.6/ltcaemodel.xml.html Instability The ratio of efferent coupling (Ce) to total coupling (Ce / (Ce + Ca)). This metric is an indicator of the package's resilience to change. The range for this metric is 0 to 1, with I=0 indicating a completely stable package and I=1 indicating a completely instable package.
